biography: Born in Czechoslovakia, studied in France, working in Germany. Using Python to get you the lowest prices online. Languages enthusiast always happy to discuss the human stuff in the IT: how humans write in their languages, how they measure time and fiddle with time zones, and how they can teach the computers to do the boring stuff for them.
